description:

As an Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases.

NOTE: This kit is designed for tubeless tires and any repairs should only be carried out on the main treaded area of the tire and NOT on the shoulder or sidewall sections. This should only used as a temporary repair to get you to a tire shop to have the tire inspected and patched internally. This is not intended to be a long-term fix or a replacement for a professional tire repair. I am only demonstrating how to use the repair kit, I have nothing to do with its design or manufacture. WARNING: Use of this product could void tire warranty. Do NOT attempt any type of tire repair if any of the following conditions exist:

‚Ä¢ The tire has less than 1.6mm tread depth
‚Ä¢ The puncture is greater than 1/4 inch diameter (6mm)
‚Ä¢ There is structural damage to tread, carcass, inner liner, or bead (including cracking, bubbling, ply separation, etc.)
‚Ä¢ The puncture is on the shoulder or sidewall of the tire
‚Ä¢ The tire has been inflated with any flammable gas
‚Ä¢ The perforating object cannot be located
‚Ä¢ The perforating object is not straight indicating the puncture path is not straight
‚Ä¢ There is little resistance felt when inserting the repair
‚Ä¢ There is evidence that the tire has been driven under-inflated
‚Ä¢ There is evidence of possible structure/internal damage
